{"tid":552730,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[導演介紹] 最有性格的導演 Wes Anderson","createTime":"2018-02-06T20:43:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T08:52:50.000Z","uid":78390,"like":34,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ea0cf8e7de17d964d7d6f7dd2fb2c0b5d24613ca","tid":552730,"uid":78390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T20:43:29.000Z","msg":"基本上求其揾一幕 都已經估到係佢拍<br />\n場景同服裝設計永遠仔細色調好似動畫 不過角色十分黑暗現實 同背景格格不入令到更特顯角色<br />\n鏡頭對稱已經好似係佢專利<br />\n對白句句都帶有點幽默 好似係本書讀出黎 （好想知佢點寫）<br />\nWes Anderson 獨一無二風格 想抄根本冇可能<br />\n<br />\nMoonrise Kingsom<br />\n兩個純真小孩為了愛私奔到世界盡頭<br />\n整部戲小朋友角度去探討愛情 家庭<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/07/043233_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F043233_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=99cef6e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/07/043248_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F043248_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=86b14f44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe Grand Budapest Hotel<br />\n算係連登常見電影<br />\n可以話史上其中一部最靚嘅電影<br />\n加上都嘅完美劇本 一班重量cast<br />\n都算係Hollywood仲keep到個Style<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/07/043328_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F043328_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b1d5af59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/07/043418_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F043418_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=87e4e28a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe Fantastic Mr. Fox<br />\n第一次進攻動畫<br />\n都幾啱Wes風格個種脱離現實嘅感覺<br />\n同本書差唔多 加插埋Wes對家庭嘅睇法<br />\n都一個幾完美嘅配搭<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/07/043614_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F043614_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3207dd76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe Darjeeling Limited<br />\n係呢度你會開始發覺 Wes主要都係寫家庭為主線<br />\n呢套講述三兄弟去印度揾返阿媽 <br />\n認真寫得唔差 而且幾番波折開解了三兄弟心結 <br />\n好窩心嘅電影<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/07/043656_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F043656_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d02ce30e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/07/043705_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F043705_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3c3a3fc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe Royal Tenenbaums<br />\n一個Prologue 已經有200個Shots 加200個埸景<br />\n講述一個父親想同返佢家人團聚 而講一個大話希望大家可以再一齊 <br />\n大家都變得陌生但係家人還是最親<br />\n呢一套算係Wes代表作 佢嘅風格都呢套開始成形<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/07/043749_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F043749_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ee8bf4b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe Life Aquatic of Steve Zissou<br />\n都係講兒子揾返佢老豆<br />\n特别有一幕 'This is my boat&quot; 我諗只有Wes咁拍 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/07/043827_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F043827_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=f6fb3578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有Rushmore 同Bottle Rocket早期製作 都十分值得睇<br />\n<br />\n今年三月Wes Anderson 會有新<br />\n第一次自己寫自己拍 同埋去返動畫界<br />\n值得留意<br />\nIsle of Dogs<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/07/044256_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F044256_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=c251ce12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a086394b3a87094c690c6e7e740b56ad43242c5c","tid":552730,"uid":37078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T00:58:18.000Z","msg":"高質post"},{"pid":"db83b8edfe7d105517c446dc393e1b88f353e2f5","tid":552730,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T01:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca5672ad30ef94fd48bbca6567c6f255e59f4535","tid":552730,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T01:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc4a79eac5b91c8408c2deaf223eca3a13f7b92a","tid":552730,"uid":85030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T05:11:58.000Z","msg":"高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a437e8118eb05a3c08eaf2baaed4488abd8c2353","tid":552730,"uid":78390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T07:01:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2Lxqzem01IU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2Lxqzem01IU&d=BHXERQ%2Buve8Ngw6OonVBHtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=f6b1d5f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2Lxqzem01IU</a><br />\n笑死已經"},{"pid":"035a56b0ae637132fe9ae632b9be9240b3f2e9ac","tid":552730,"uid":48479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a437e8118eb05a3c08eaf2baaed4488abd8c2353","tid":552730,"uid":78390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T07:01:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2Lxqzem01IU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https